        </div>
        <div class="card rounded-2xl p-6 reveal relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-cyan-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">2</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 mt-2">Escopo & Proposta</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Definição clara das funcionalidades do sistema, prazos de entrega e valores.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card rounded-2xl p-6 reveal relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-cyan-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">3</div>
